Interactive 3D graphs

library(rgl)
volc <- list(x = 10 * 1:ncol(volcano), y = 10 * 1:nrow(volcano), z = 5 * volcano)
surface3d(volc$y, volc$x, volc$z, terrain.colors(max(volcano))[volcano])
